msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"Use a side hop to avoid enemy attacks.\n"
"This will create an opening that you\n"
"can use to strike back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"Do a backflip to avoid enemy attacks\n"
"and create an opening to strike back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"You can repel an attack if you parry with\n"
"your shield at just the right time. Strike\n"
"back in the opening you create."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"Build up your power, and then release it\n"
"to unleash a charge attack. Catch your\n"
"enemies in this motion to damage them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"You have done well to learn these crucial\n"
"skills. Now, proceed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"You cannot practice this skill without a\n"
"shield. Prepare yourself and try again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"You cannot practice this skill without a\n"
"weapon. Prepare yourself and try again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"Offer before me a block of ice. Only then\n"
"will the path forward open."
msgstr ""

